name: inPresenceOfExcludeAnnotationsTheClassInfoObjectShouldContainAValidSetOfPojoAttributes

testSteps.description: Given a Set of annotations to be excluded
Given a ClassInfo with excluded annotations and excluded fields
Then the Object should not be null
Then the attributes contains in ClassInfo should match the ones contains in the POJO

title: The ClassInfo object created for a class should handle @PodamExcludeAnnotations
